{"tid":2151081,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"演唱會公開驚喜！TWICE 將發行《MORE & MORE》英文版！","createTime":"2020-08-11T08:24:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T19:53:36.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b317180f06ef7fe1ee912d581baff0283b0fa6d8","tid":2151081,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T08:24:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.kpopn.com/upload/3ddf4b5c4dee81d1e926.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kpopn.com%2Fupload%2F3ddf4b5c4dee81d1e926.jpg&h=38487101&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTWICE 在線上演唱會實驚喜宣布將發行《MORE &amp; MORE》英文版！<br />\n<br />\n8月9日，TWICE 透過 V LIVE 舉辦了線上演唱會《Beyond LIVE &ndash; TWICE: World in A Day》，在帶來她們最新主打歌MORE &amp; MORE》的舞台後，志效說有個驚喜要告訴粉絲們，Mina 接著公開細節：「英文版《MORE &amp; MORE》即將發行！」<br />\n<br />\n整場演唱會，TWICE 帶來了《FANCY》、《Heart Shaker》、《TT》等熱門曲目，也首度帶來了《LOVE FOOLISH》舞台，對於這次的初舞台，SANA 說：「我真的很緊張，但多虧了 ONCE 的正面迴響才能做的好。」<br />\n<br />\n儘管因為疫情關係，TWICE 沒能親自與粉絲見面，TWICE 還是透過螢幕與粉絲們互動，也在演唱會中讀了粉絲留言。彩瑛還透露，自己因為首次進行線上演唱會感到緊張：「然而，因為這真的感覺很像還是跟 ONCE 一起舉辦演唱會，我的擔心消失了。」MOMO 也說：「在這裡可以感受到 ONCE 的能量與熱情真的很開心。」而定延因為健康問題，坐著參與演唱會。<br />\n<br />\n接下來，就讓我們一起期待英文版的《MORE &amp; MORE》吧！"},{"pid":"1705ee8c7340324784992f80b2c6ce82fb324faa","tid":2151081,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T08:26:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i2.tcafe2a.com/2008/20200811020734_cececa2d23d4e422a698225f196ad427_osyu.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi2.tcafe2a.com%2F2008%2F20200811020734_cececa2d23d4e422a698225f196ad427_osyu.gif&h=e815446d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i2.tcafe2a.com/2008/20200811020738_cececa2d23d4e422a698225f196ad427_wr0z.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi2.tcafe2a.com%2F2008%2F20200811020738_cececa2d23d4e422a698225f196ad427_wr0z.gif&h=d40a153a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i2.tcafe2a.com/2008/20200811020744_cececa2d23d4e422a698225f196ad427_c2k8.gif\" d